{"tid":2192251,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"裁判官何俊堯調職處理高院刑事案排期 七月前已決定非突然","createTime":"2020-09-07T04:02:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-07T04:55:30.000Z","uid":365024,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"4637ae9f440533e70d089cf30913f8a2b5100808","tid":2192251,"uid":365024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T04:02:35.000Z","msg":"根據司法機構網頁顯示，何官將調任高等法院刑事案件排期法官，惟據知調職的決定並非突然，<span class=\"x-large\"><strong><span class=\"red\">實早於今年七月之前已定，與投訴無關，而過往亦有多位裁判官曾任該職位。</span></strong></span><br />\n翻查資料，過往<ins><span class=\"red\"><strong>裁判官杜浩成及張天雁曾擔任此職位</strong></span></ins>，兩人現分別於觀塘及九龍城裁判法院審案。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200907/YG4HMREFEJDLBJT6QP5REKMRSU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200907%2FYG4HMREFEJDLBJT6QP5REKMRSU%2F&d=YmBpLFXYotmGfWLbQLkNpwNVisxpnNpADW7ISUiLTyw%3D&h=3b651076\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200907%2FYG4HMREFEJDLBJT6QP5REKMRSU%2F&h=351ae3fa\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200907/YG4HMREFEJDLBJT6QP5REKMRSU/</a>"},{"pid":"1c78800f18fd5dcf7c53508e2ad93a4fe342bb87","tid":2192251,"uid":365024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T04:55:30.000Z","msg":"翻查資料，由中聯辦控制的《大公報》、大公文匯集團高層持股的網媒「點新聞」近一個月先後發文引述不具名的市民、公眾批評司法機構，也曾經點名批評何俊堯在內的五名裁判官以及法官，形容他們是「黃官」，「放生暴徒『着草』」，又指「公眾」質疑他們破壞法治。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E4%BD%95%E4%BF%8A%E5%A0%AF%E8%AA%BF%E8%81%B7-%E4%B8%AD%E8%81%AF%E8%BE%A6%E6%8E%A7%E5%88%B6%E5%AA%92%E9%AB%94%E9%A0%BB%E7%99%BC%E5%8A%9F-%E9%BB%9E%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E-%E6%9B%BE%E8%BD%9F%E4%BA%94-%E9%BB%83%E5%AE%98-%E6%94%BE%E7%94%9F%E6%9A%B4%E5%BE%92%E7%9D%80%E8%8D%89/?fbclid=IwAR3w58UGEfNk3P9PvV9LFIUb8aWW6KcnV1txevHa4YFgQs3zYUoPVer0ngw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E4%25BD%2595%25E4%25BF%258A%25E5%25A0%25AF%25E8%25A